---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const updated = 'April 24, 2026';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — ParentCompass"
  description="How ParentCompass collects, uses, and protects your personal information."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="bg-sand-50 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">

      <p class="text-terra-500 text-xs font-sans font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-forest-800 mb-3">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-stone-400 text-sm font-sans mb-12">Last updated: {updated}</p>

      <div class="prose-legal">

        <h2>1. Who we are</h2>
        <p>
          ParentCompass (<strong>parentcompass.ai</strong>) is an AI-powered college counselling service
          for families. References to "we", "us", or "ParentCompass" in this policy refer to the
          team operating parentcompass.ai. For privacy enquiries, contact us at
          <a href="mailto:hello@parentcompass.ai">hello@parentcompass.ai</a>.
        </p>

        <h2>2. What data we collect</h2>
        <p>At this stage, ParentCompass is a pre-launch product. We collect only:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Email address</strong> — when you join our waitlist via the form on our homepage.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          We do not collect your name, phone number, payment information, or any other personal
          data unless you provide it voluntarily by emailing us.
        </p>

        <h2>3. How we use your data</h2>
        <p>Your email address is used solely to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Notify you when ParentCompass launches</li>
          <li>Send you early-access information and founding-member pricing details</li>
          <li>Occasionally share product updates relevant to ParentCompass</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We will never sell, rent, or share your email address with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>

        <h2>4. Third-party services</h2>
        <p>We use the following services to operate our waitlist:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>MailerLite</strong> — our email service provider. Your email address is stored
            on MailerLite's servers. MailerLite's privacy policy is available at
            <a href="https://www.mailerlite.com/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">mailerlite.com</a>.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Vercel</strong> — our website hosting provider. Vercel may collect standard
            server logs (IP address, browser type) for security and performance purposes.
            Vercel's privacy policy is available at
            <a href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">vercel.com</a>.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>5. Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          Our website does not use tracking cookies or advertising cookies. Vercel may set
          technical cookies necessary for website delivery. We do not use cookies to track
          you across other websites.
        </p>

        <h2>6. Your rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Unsubscribe</strong> — click the unsubscribe link in any email we send you</li>
          <li><strong>Access</strong> — request a copy of the data we hold about you</li>
          <li><strong>Delete</strong> — request that we delete your email address from our list</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          To exercise any of these rights, email us at
          <a href="mailto:hello@parentcompass.ai">hello@parentcompass.ai</a> and we will
          respond within 7 days.
        </p>

        <h2>7. Data retention</h2>
        <p>
          We retain your email address on our waitlist until you unsubscribe or request deletion.
          If ParentCompass does not launch within 24 months of you joining the waitlist, we will
          delete all waitlist data.
        </p>

        <h2>8. Children's privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Our waitlist is intended for parents and adults aged 18 and over. We do not knowingly
          collect personal data from children under 13. If you believe a child has submitted
          their data to us, contact us at
          <a href="mailto:hello@parentcompass.ai">hello@parentcompass.ai</a> and we will
          delete it promptly.
        </p>

        <h2>9. Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this policy as the product evolves. We will notify waitlist members by
          email of any material changes. Continued use of our site after changes constitutes
          acceptance of the updated policy.
        </p>

        <h2>10. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about this policy? Email us at
          <a href="mailto:hello@parentcompass.ai">hello@parentcompass.ai</a>.
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .prose-legal h2 {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1A3A2A;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .prose-legal p {
    font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: #6B5F4E;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .prose-legal ul {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .prose-legal li {
    font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: #6B5F4E;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  .prose-legal a {
    color: #C4603A;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  .prose-legal strong {
    color: #4A3F32;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
